          <p class='first-para'>
            It is clear from the hon. Lady's remark about mumbling over coffee that she is not aware that the director of the Wellcome Trust, in his evidence to the Science and Technology Committee, of which I am a member, gave a full and clear account of the reasons why the trust favoured the Rutherford Appleton Laboratory.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0347P0-04812'>
        <a name='S6CV0347P0_20000329_WH_20'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-helen-southworth' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0347P0_20000329_WH_20' title='Link to this speech by Ms Helen Southworth' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
